{"tid":845432,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"花生！傳美斯碧基決裂","createTime":"2018-10-02T15:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T03:26:14.000Z","uid":54109,"like":175,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"a0569cab8231001128f34be141e816f32293a82a","tid":845432,"uid":54109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:42:25.000Z","msg":"巴塞隆拿最近戰績低迷，有傳美斯、碧基2名攻守大將更爆發不和。<br />\n<br />\n周一西班牙電視節目《El Chiringuito de Jugones》爆料，巴塞隆拿近3場不勝，只得2和1負，引起了更衣室內亂，前鋒美斯（Lionel Messi）及中堅碧基2名大佬輩，雖然從青年軍已合作，但關係已決裂。<br />\n<br />\n該節目指，碧基不滿美斯今季成為了隊長，卻很少跟傳媒對話及接受訪問。知情人士表示：「碧基批評美斯在球會陷困難時，不會挺身而出面對傳媒，更指他只會在離開歐洲，跟隨阿根廷國家隊時才會發聲。」<br />\n<br />\n至於美斯亦對碧基不滿，認為對方要為巴塞近期差勁的戰績負責任。據知，美斯已當面批評碧基，指由他領導的防線未能好好保護龍門，讓對手攻入太多球。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=RqU6pVPmSc1SWWoYufi87TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=678c0cd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.balls.ie/uploads/2013/05/i1QkBKsxbQDye.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.balls.ie%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F05%2Fi1QkBKsxbQDye.gif&h=c4d2caf9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea443de747052460e3726e3ecdbe873d72efa24c","tid":845432,"uid":68916,"like":224,"dislike":59,"score":165,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:44:45.000Z","msg":"當一個人係國家隊同球會都可以有咁多內訌<br />\n問題嘅根源已經好明顯"},{"pid":"b78a613b1efe4d1dce691516d130305901f2a84a","tid":845432,"uid":34852,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:45:47.000Z","msg":"傳獌外傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2dcdb49b701f5748598767c95aa8ed06693bc97","tid":845432,"uid":34293,"like":72,"dislike":1,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T16:08:55.000Z","msg":"碧基去做主席啦  唔好再係球場獻醜啦"},{"pid":"cb3fbc129064e803826517ddd3b527c62f899694","tid":845432,"uid":58811,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T16:10:55.000Z","msg":"呢個閪班牙節目仲濕鳩過東張西望<img src=\"/assets/